   - "Is 'fast loading' quantified with specific timing thresholds? [Clarity, Spec \xA7NFR-2]"
   - "Are 'related episodes' selection criteria explicitly defined? [Clarity, Spec \xA7FR-5]"
   - "Is 'prominent' defined with measurable visual properties? [Ambiguity, Spec \xA7FR-4]"

